TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SEQ_00Qhoterl Pasol is attempting, unsuccessfully, to close her nostrils.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SEQ_00 Schwierigkeitsanpassung (Job/Klasse darf nicht gewechselt werden)

Qhoterl Pasol will für Sauberkeit sorgen.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SEQ_01<tab>Deliver the requested items to Qhoterl Pasol.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SEQ_01<tab>Qhoterl Pasol die gewünschte Ware bringen

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Mine splendid natron in the depths of Lake Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Deliver the splendid natron to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Gather splendid marimo in the depths of Lake Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Deliver the splendid marimo to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Spearfish a splendid sponge in the depths of Lake Tusi Mek'ta)) ((Deliver the splendid sponge to Qhoterl Pasol)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_TODO_00<tab><var 08 E4E80511 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Im Tusi Mek'ta <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> herausbrechen)) ((Qhoterl Pasol das <var 28 ((Item)) E8060A /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80512 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Im Tusi Mek'ta <var 32 ((Item)) 06E806030502 /var> ernten)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 03E806030502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80513 ((<var 08 E3E802E803 ((Im Tusi Mek'ta <var 32 ((Item)) 02E806020502 /var> fangen)) ((Qhoterl Pasol <var 32 ((Item)) 03E806020502 /var> bringen)) /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var>)) /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Sometimes I wish I didn't have such a sensitive nose. When the workers come back from the caves, they carry with them the most pungent of odors! It really is quite unbearable!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Ganz schlimmer Zustand ist hier, ganz schlimm! Was ist, fragst du? Siehst du doch, wie alles schmutzig ist von rückkehrenden Suchenden!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Unfortunately, even a thorough scrubbing with warm water does little to remove the stench. I fear there is little choice but to resort to a rarely used treatment, and as you can imagine, the ingredients required are also rather rare themselves...
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Qitari lieben Sauberkeit. So viel Schmutz ist Schande!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>First, I'll need roughly three pinches of natron. Your cooperation will be most appreciated, I assure you!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_010<tab>Qhoterl will Schmutzfinken ordentliche Dusche verpassen. Dafür braucht Qhoterl drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27356030502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta. Kannst du solche mitbringen, ja?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>First, I'll need roughly three marimo. Your cooperation will be most appreciated, I assure you!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_020<tab>Qhoterl will Schmutzfinken ordentliche Dusche verpassen. Dafür braucht Qhoterl drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27370030502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta. Kannst du solche mitbringen, ja?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>First, I'll need a sponge, the living sort, but you'll need to hook the little scoundrel with your spear as they're far too crafty to take any bait. Your cooperation will be most appreciated, I assure you!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030<tab>Qhoterl will Schmutzfinken ordentliche Dusche verpassen. Dafür braucht Qhoterl <var 32 ((Item)) 06F2738A020502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta. Kannst du mitbringen, ja?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SYSTEM_100_040<tab>In order to proceed with this quest, you must first complete the quest “A New Fishing Ex-spear-ience” and unlock spearfishing.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_SYSTEM_100_040<tab>Um diesen Auftrag spielen zu können, muss das Speerfischen im Auftrag „Wie ein Fischer im Wasser“ erlernt worden sein.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>Oh! I forgot to mention that you'll need to dive into the waters of Lake Tusi Mek'ta to find it!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_040<tab>Bringst du Qhoterl drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27356030502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta, ja? Dann wird Dreck endlich Sache von Ver<var 16 /var>gangen<var 16 /var>heit sein.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Oh! I forgot to mention that you'll need to dive into the waters of Lake Tusi Mek'ta to find them!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_050<tab>Bringst du Qhoterl drei <var 32 ((Item)) 06F27370030502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta, ja? Dann wird Dreck endlich Sache von Ver<var 16 /var>gangen<var 16 /var>heit sein.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>It seems that Lake Tusi Mek'ta is relatively free of large, flesh-eating beasts, so your chances of being devoured alive are actually quite low! Welcome news, I'm sure!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_060<tab>Bringst du Qhoterl <var 32 ((Item)) 06F2738A020502 /var> aus Schlangensee Tusi Mek'ta, ja? Dann wird Dreck endlich Sache von Ver<var 16 /var>gangen<var 16 /var>heit sein.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Have you brought what I asked for? Please say you have!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_070<tab>Ach, Qhoterl kann Dreck nicht mehr sehen! Furchtbarer Zustand, ja! Hast du mitgebracht, worum Qhoterl gebeten hat?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Marvelous! Once the concoction is ready, those reeking reprobates will be the very pinnacle of cleanliness in just a few scrubs!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_080<tab>Ooh, vielen Dank! Bald werden alle strahlen vor Sauberkeit. Und Qhoterl strahlt auch!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_081<tab>At the top of my list of candidates are my husband and son. Their combined stench is enough to curdle milk!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ112_03817_QHOTERLPASOL_000_081<tab>So, als Erstes werden eigener Ehemann und Sohn gewaschen, ha! Sind am schmutzigsten von allen, von Ohren bis hinunter zu Krallen! Puh!
